1
00:00:00,060 --> 00:00:05,100
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,100 --> 00:00:10,220
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,220 --> 00:00:15,380
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,380 --> 00:00:22,780
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,620 --> 00:00:30,740
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,740 --> 00:00:35,620
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,860 --> 00:00:40,300
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,860 --> 00:00:49,660
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,980 --> 00:00:54,300
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:59,420
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,740 --> 00:01:03,420
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:06,020
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:10,140
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:14,740
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,580 --> 00:01:20,100
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,140 --> 00:01:23,900
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,900 --> 00:01:26,500
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,780 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 68 =

20
00:01:33,820 --> 00:01:34,940
Are you crazy, Minister Han?

21
00:01:35,520 --> 00:01:37,110
If you tell His Majesty who Huaiji is,

22
00:01:37,350 --> 00:01:39,160
you’ll make him feel worse.

23
00:01:41,370 --> 00:01:42,360
When he feels worse,

24
00:01:42,670 --> 00:01:44,860
maybe he’ll make up his mind

25
00:01:45,020 --> 00:01:45,950
and make a final decision

26
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:47,350
instead of hesitating.

27
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:48,380
What?

28
00:01:49,150 --> 00:01:50,170
His Majesty

29
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:52,090
doesn’t want to sacrifice Huaiji

30
00:01:52,620 --> 00:01:54,520
or stimulate Princess.

31
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:56,630
Yet he also wants to maintain
the reputation and honor

32
00:01:56,850 --> 00:01:57,790
for Princess.

33
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,000
He’s been in a dilemma.

34
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:01,180
So, he wants to put it off

35
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:02,910
until censors give up

36
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:05,270
because there’s no hope.

37
00:02:06,750 --> 00:02:07,900
It may work.

38
00:02:09,570 --> 00:02:12,380
When His Majesty confronts his officials,

39
00:02:12,900 --> 00:02:14,490
he doesn’t care for politics.

40
00:02:17,270 --> 00:02:19,090
There’s an important issue

41
00:02:20,270 --> 00:02:21,140
that can no longer wait.

42
00:02:23,450 --> 00:02:24,620
No longer wait?

43
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,150
Han Qi.

44
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:29,390
Aren’t you letting His Majesty down

45
00:02:29,390 --> 00:02:30,480
for his care over the years?

46
00:02:35,250 --> 00:02:36,190
We both know

47
00:02:36,550 --> 00:02:39,460
His Majesty cares the most for

48
00:02:39,460 --> 00:02:40,930
the peace of our nation.

49
00:02:41,820 --> 00:02:43,740
His Majesty is always sick and has no son.

50
00:02:44,020 --> 00:02:46,240
Without a son, our nation is in danger.

51
00:02:47,150 --> 00:02:49,700
As his official, I must try my best

52
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:52,260
to defend what His Majesty cares for.

53
00:02:52,900 --> 00:02:54,940
When His Majesty is confused,

54
00:02:55,350 --> 00:02:56,540
I’ll do everything possible to

55
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:59,360
help him get over the problem.

56
00:03:05,370 --> 00:03:08,390
Liang Huaiji has done countless crimes.

57
00:03:15,900 --> 00:03:17,390
Huaiji is a mere eunuch.

58
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:19,120
How can he do countless crimes?

59
00:03:20,100 --> 00:03:21,040
How does Sima Guang write about

60
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:22,250
those evil guys

61
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,300
who have betrayed our nation?

62
00:03:30,670 --> 00:03:32,350
He still submits a proposal a day.

63
00:03:33,050 --> 00:03:36,510
Should he copy it every day?

64
00:03:39,020 --> 00:03:40,170
Sima Guang wrote a different proposal

65
00:03:40,170 --> 00:03:41,370
every day,

66
00:03:41,670 --> 00:03:43,410
complaining about different crimes.

67
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,170
Over the past days,

68
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,570
a girl like Huirou

69
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:48,730
and a eunuch like Huaiji

70
00:03:48,970 --> 00:03:49,940
seem to have done

71
00:03:49,940 --> 00:03:51,800
every possible crime in this world.

72
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:00,500
What’s up?

73
00:04:03,270 --> 00:04:05,920
Minister Han submitted a secret proposal.

74
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,070
Han Qi?

75
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:11,250
Secret?

76
00:04:42,470 --> 00:04:43,370
Huaiji is the younger son of

77
00:04:47,220 --> 00:04:48,620
the Liang family?

78
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:52,650
Yes.

79
00:05:13,970 --> 00:05:15,230
Bring Han Qi

80
00:05:17,220 --> 00:05:18,560
to me.

81
00:05:22,100 --> 00:05:23,650
Your Majesty, you asked me

82
00:05:23,950 --> 00:05:25,250
to look for Mrs. Liang

83
00:05:25,250 --> 00:05:26,660
and her two sons

84
00:05:27,020 --> 00:05:28,000
so that I could help them.

85
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,950
I did look everywhere for them.

86
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,250
But their house

87
00:05:33,270 --> 00:05:34,720
was sold to a foreign salesman.

88
00:05:35,470 --> 00:05:37,540
No neighbors knew where they had gone.

89
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,720
I checked where Mrs. Liang was born

90
00:05:40,050 --> 00:05:41,060
and tracked down to Suzhou.

91
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:44,070
But they had moved away.

92
00:05:45,270 --> 00:05:46,440
Without any more clues,

93
00:05:46,750 --> 00:05:47,780
I had to give up.

94
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,890
But years later,

95
00:05:50,250 --> 00:05:52,000
I met Yuansheng in Restaurant of Breeze.

96
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,950
I knew

97
00:05:57,500 --> 00:05:58,830
what Yuansheng did.

98
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,680
But how could Yuanheng

99
00:06:06,270 --> 00:06:07,650
be Huaiji?

100
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:15,450
Yuansheng made a scene at the county government.

101
00:06:15,450 --> 00:06:17,560
He exposed many corrupt or incompetent officials.

102
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,160
It startled the imperial court.

103
00:06:20,100 --> 00:06:21,340
But at that time,

104
00:06:21,870 --> 00:06:22,620
Yuanheng had been

105
00:06:23,950 --> 00:06:25,560
sold by his aunt.

106
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,350
When I found him,

107
00:06:27,870 --> 00:06:29,400
he had been admitted as a eunuch.

108
00:06:30,170 --> 00:06:30,940
In this case,

109
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:34,270
no officers were against the rule.

110
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:37,020
But if Yuansheng knew

111
00:06:37,250 --> 00:06:39,260
it was related to corrupt officials,

112
00:06:40,020 --> 00:06:42,840
there could be big trouble again.

113
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,460
And...

114
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,570
And...

115
00:06:49,470 --> 00:06:50,460
I know.

116
00:06:51,870 --> 00:06:52,700
You...

117
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,010
Both of you...

118
00:06:57,400 --> 00:06:59,040
You don’t want me to know.

119
00:07:01,381 --> 00:07:04,310
Because I was capricious at a young age,

120
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:07,770
I made the Liang brothers lose their father.

121
00:07:09,100 --> 00:07:09,880
Then,

122
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,530
because of the redundant,

123
00:07:13,530 --> 00:07:14,870
corrupt and incompetent officials,

124
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,430
the younger son of the Liang family

125
00:07:18,850 --> 00:07:20,700
was castrated.

126
00:07:26,470 --> 00:07:30,440
If Huaiji hadn’t been castrated,

127
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:34,730
he would have passed the imperial exam

128
00:07:35,750 --> 00:07:37,290
and have become an upright official

129
00:07:37,290 --> 00:07:39,010
who cared for people.

130
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:47,270
Your Majesty, there were coincidences.

131
00:07:48,420 --> 00:07:50,340
Everyone has his fate.

132
00:07:51,750 --> 00:07:53,350
Don’t be too sad

133
00:07:54,570 --> 00:07:55,590
for this.

134
00:07:58,320 --> 00:08:00,440
Your Majesty, I tell you this,

135
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:04,340
only because censors impeach Princess

136
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:06,840
and condemn Huaiji.

137
00:08:08,670 --> 00:08:09,590
They want to severely punish him

138
00:08:10,850 --> 00:08:12,470
and even kill him.

139
00:08:18,770 --> 00:08:20,170
I never want to

140
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,230
kill Huaiji

141
00:08:25,770 --> 00:08:27,550
to stop censors from complaining.

142
00:08:43,370 --> 00:08:44,140
Mr. Zhang.

143
00:08:48,300 --> 00:08:49,300
Go to the palace with me.

144
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:18,800
= Sima Guang, courtesy name Junshi =

145
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:19,630
Your Majesty,

146
00:09:19,630 --> 00:09:21,230
please reject Prince Consort’s application.

147
00:09:21,670 --> 00:09:23,090
Please cancel the order to transfer him

148
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:24,820
and teach Princess to

149
00:09:25,350 --> 00:09:27,180
look after her mother-in-law
and respect her husband.

150
00:09:27,670 --> 00:09:29,300
Please severely punish Eunuch Liang Huaiji.

151
00:09:31,050 --> 00:09:33,070
For glory and power,

152
00:09:33,650 --> 00:09:34,670
Liang Huaiji drove a wedge between them,

153
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,590
humiliated Princess

154
00:09:37,050 --> 00:09:38,260
and defamed Your Majesty.

155
00:09:39,070 --> 00:09:40,180
With heinous crimes,

156
00:09:41,470 --> 00:09:42,350
he deserves to be killed!

157
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:52,960
Your Majesty, before you kill Liang Huaiji,

158
00:09:53,100 --> 00:09:55,000
Princess won’t get away from evilness,

159
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,090
or forget her delusion

160
00:09:56,350 --> 00:09:58,910
so that she’ll be a good wife

161
00:09:58,910 --> 00:10:00,640
as an example for all girls of our nation.

162
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:03,130
= Wang Tao, courtesy name Ledao =
This is the right way you should teach your daughter.

163
00:10:06,300 --> 00:10:08,410
Your Majesty, please kill Liang Huaiji

164
00:10:08,700 --> 00:10:09,880
to avoid public censure.

165
00:10:19,420 --> 00:10:22,500
Your Majesty, I’ve brought Liang Huaiji to you.

166
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:36,340
Huaiji, come.

167
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:41,900
Come. Yuanheng. Come to me.

168
00:10:48,450 --> 00:10:50,660
Your original name is Liang Yuanheng.

169
00:10:51,770 --> 00:10:53,420
You became Huaiji after you worked here.

170
00:10:54,570 --> 00:10:56,940
From now on, you’ll still use your original name.

171
00:10:57,500 --> 00:10:59,300
The name your parents picked for you.

172
00:11:09,870 --> 00:11:10,750
Come, Yuanheng.

173
00:11:27,870 --> 00:11:28,590
Yuanheng.

174
00:11:31,150 --> 00:11:31,980
Face them.

175
00:11:39,850 --> 00:11:40,830
Turn to them.

176
00:11:41,400 --> 00:11:43,520
Don’t be scared. I’m with you.

177
00:12:05,050 --> 00:12:05,940
This is the eunuch

178
00:12:05,940 --> 00:12:07,470
you ask me to kill.

179
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,540
Look carefully at him.

180
00:12:11,500 --> 00:12:13,040
Is he the evil man

181
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:14,900
who you think drove a wedge

182
00:12:15,270 --> 00:12:17,710
between my daughter and her husband

183
00:12:17,950 --> 00:12:19,760
only to get power from her?

184
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:22,380
How can we judge a man by his appearance?

185
00:12:23,470 --> 00:12:24,880
Man’s heart is incomprehensible,

186
00:12:25,500 --> 00:12:26,350
just because some evil guys

187
00:12:26,350 --> 00:12:27,890
may also look kind.

188
00:12:30,220 --> 00:12:31,340
If he weren’t evil,

189
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:34,030
he wouldn’t have approached Princess,

190
00:12:34,030 --> 00:12:35,630
seduced her or driven a wedge between her family

191
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:38,900
in the name of her eunuch?

192
00:12:39,920 --> 00:12:42,990
Well, how do you judge

193
00:12:43,620 --> 00:12:44,850
he’s an evil man?

194
00:12:46,370 --> 00:12:47,730
Princess quarreled with Prince Consort.

195
00:12:48,020 --> 00:12:49,200
Isn’t that clear evidence?

196
00:12:55,450 --> 00:12:58,210
There are many eunuchs in Princess’s Mansion.

197
00:12:58,700 --> 00:13:00,130
When Princess quarreled with her husband,

198
00:13:00,820 --> 00:13:02,180
main servants and maids in her mansion

199
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:04,610
should all be blamed.

200
00:13:05,700 --> 00:13:07,560
I’ve demoted Liang Quanyi,

201
00:13:07,850 --> 00:13:09,160
banished wet nurse Madam Han.

202
00:13:09,800 --> 00:13:13,120
Yuanheng was exiled to Luoyang for nearly a year.

203
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:14,790
I think

204
00:13:15,350 --> 00:13:17,540
they’ve had enough punishment.

205
00:13:21,670 --> 00:13:23,080
Your Majesty,

206
00:13:24,550 --> 00:13:25,960
do you really want me to talk about

207
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:29,160
princess’s unethical behaviors here?

208
00:13:47,420 --> 00:13:49,780
You put gauze

209
00:13:49,780 --> 00:13:51,440
on Huirou’s unethical behaviors

210
00:13:52,820 --> 00:13:54,450
you have imagined

211
00:13:54,620 --> 00:13:56,430
and hold it up in public.

212
00:13:56,850 --> 00:13:58,350
You salute to me

213
00:13:58,350 --> 00:13:59,760
and call me a wise emperor.

214
00:13:59,850 --> 00:14:01,110
But you think I’m cheated by evil guys.

215
00:14:01,870 --> 00:14:04,820
If I don’t take your advice

216
00:14:04,900 --> 00:14:06,480
to kill the so-called evil man,

217
00:14:07,250 --> 00:14:09,360
you’re going to remove the gauze

218
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:12,050
and expose her unethical behaviors, right?

219
00:14:15,070 --> 00:14:16,470
Your Majesty,

220
00:14:18,020 --> 00:14:19,670
if you think I’m forcing you,

221
00:14:21,100 --> 00:14:22,870
you can punish me for disrespecting.

222
00:14:24,300 --> 00:14:25,750
But I admonish against whatever mistake I know.

223
00:14:26,650 --> 00:14:28,820
This is my duty as a censor.

224
00:14:30,020 --> 00:14:31,440
I can’t neglect my job,

225
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:32,720
only because I’m scared of punishment.

226
00:14:36,370 --> 00:14:37,650
Admonish against whatever mistake you know?

227
00:14:39,920 --> 00:14:40,850
Who do you think

228
00:14:42,320 --> 00:14:43,540
made the mistake?

229
00:14:57,870 --> 00:14:59,530
Princess did unethical behaviors.

230
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:02,990
But Your Majesty,

231
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,440
you pampered her.

232
00:15:08,920 --> 00:15:10,160
Eunuch Liang Huaiji is the chief criminal

233
00:15:10,160 --> 00:15:11,950
who brings the blame to you.

234
00:15:11,970 --> 00:15:12,780
I think

235
00:15:14,070 --> 00:15:15,470
he must be killed

236
00:15:16,970 --> 00:15:17,960
for his fault.

237
00:15:38,570 --> 00:15:39,310
No.

238
00:15:41,070 --> 00:15:42,070
He isn’t the chief criminal.

239
00:15:43,050 --> 00:15:44,110
He made some mistakes,

240
00:15:46,050 --> 00:15:48,080
only because he was eager to defend Huirou.

241
00:15:48,850 --> 00:15:50,260
Failing to persuade Huirou,

242
00:15:50,450 --> 00:15:51,730
he had to follow her

243
00:15:52,650 --> 00:15:53,460
so that he could protect Princess

244
00:15:53,460 --> 00:15:55,250
who he watched her growing up.

245
00:15:58,084 --> 00:15:59,450
Your Majesty,

246
00:16:01,120 --> 00:16:02,520
who do you think is the chief criminal?

247
00:16:08,900 --> 00:16:13,960
I don’t think there’s a chief criminal.

248
00:16:21,950 --> 00:16:25,590
There are only unlucky people.

249
00:16:27,195 --> 00:16:29,490
Princess didn’t get on well with Prince Consort,

250
00:16:30,170 --> 00:16:31,860
not because of someone else,

251
00:16:32,750 --> 00:16:36,080
but because they didn’t love each other.

252
00:16:38,270 --> 00:16:39,410
Huaiji didn’t

253
00:16:42,070 --> 00:16:45,940
seduce princess.

254
00:16:46,500 --> 00:16:48,050
He just admired her.

255
00:16:48,970 --> 00:16:51,960
Seeing Princess being sad and worried,

256
00:16:52,450 --> 00:16:55,540
he had no choice, but to keep her company.

257
00:16:58,350 --> 00:16:59,400
His Majesty.

258
00:17:03,070 --> 00:17:06,330
His Majesty thought he picked a very good husband

259
00:17:07,120 --> 00:17:09,730
for Princess.

260
00:17:11,370 --> 00:17:14,780
Unexpectedly, Princess becomes more haggard.

261
00:17:16,170 --> 00:17:19,580
Failing to persuade her,

262
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:22,720
Your Majesty doesn’t have the heart

263
00:17:23,300 --> 00:17:25,980
to see her give up her life.

264
00:17:30,650 --> 00:17:32,700
Scholar Ouyang, are you going to cover
all the mistakes

265
00:17:32,700 --> 00:17:34,430
only with this excuse?

266
00:17:36,100 --> 00:17:39,550
If it works, do we not need laws,

267
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:41,340
punishment

268
00:17:42,170 --> 00:17:43,650
or prison?

269
00:17:45,100 --> 00:17:49,150
When a government tries a case,

270
00:17:49,850 --> 00:17:52,220
there should be a victim, right?

271
00:17:53,900 --> 00:17:55,360
When someone loses money,

272
00:17:56,120 --> 00:17:58,560
we find the thief and punish him.

273
00:17:59,450 --> 00:18:00,800
When someone is dead,

274
00:18:01,620 --> 00:18:03,930
we find the murderer and execute him.

275
00:18:05,620 --> 00:18:07,580
Princess doesn’t respect her mother-in-law.

276
00:18:08,300 --> 00:18:11,360
His Majesty has punished her servants

277
00:18:11,360 --> 00:18:12,570
for their careless work.

278
00:18:13,470 --> 00:18:16,290
Liang Quanyi and inferior servants are exiled,

279
00:18:16,320 --> 00:18:18,530
to comfort Mrs. Yang.

280
00:18:19,450 --> 00:18:23,770
As for the unhappy life between the couple,

281
00:18:25,700 --> 00:18:29,210
they’ve both made mistakes.

282
00:18:29,820 --> 00:18:32,350
They are victims.

283
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:37,340
Now, Prince Consort asks to be transferred

284
00:18:38,150 --> 00:18:41,180
just because he wants to end the misfortune.

285
00:18:43,270 --> 00:18:47,010
Censor Sima, why do you want to stop him?

286
00:18:49,520 --> 00:18:51,790
To satisfy His Majesty,

287
00:18:53,420 --> 00:18:54,860
you even distort the truth.

288
00:18:56,270 --> 00:18:58,440
Don’t you feel ashamed?

289
00:19:01,500 --> 00:19:04,270
Your Majesty, no one knew

290
00:19:04,270 --> 00:19:05,800
what happened to Li Wei and Princess.

291
00:19:06,150 --> 00:19:07,020
You and Princess

292
00:19:07,270 --> 00:19:09,070
shall decide what to do yourselves.

293
00:19:09,350 --> 00:19:11,120
Censors shouldn’t have complained.

294
00:19:11,600 --> 00:19:13,610
But Prince Consort impeaches himself for
no mistake.

295
00:19:13,850 --> 00:19:16,750
And you agree to transfer him.

296
00:19:17,050 --> 00:19:18,540
Meanwhile, the guilty eunuch comes back.

297
00:19:18,600 --> 00:19:20,270
We’re surprised to hear that

298
00:19:20,370 --> 00:19:22,060
and we can’t help guessing.

299
00:19:22,470 --> 00:19:23,400
I believe,

300
00:19:23,650 --> 00:19:26,030
Princess is gentle and careful

301
00:19:26,030 --> 00:19:27,050
because she was brought up by you.

302
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:28,780
She couldn’t do anything improper.

303
00:19:29,100 --> 00:19:31,530
But when people talk about it,

304
00:19:31,750 --> 00:19:33,960
rumors always go around.

305
00:19:34,220 --> 00:19:36,200
So, I sincerely beg you

306
00:19:36,300 --> 00:19:37,680
to defend her marriage

307
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:39,100
and keep Prince Consort in city.

308
00:19:39,770 --> 00:19:41,460
As for Eunuch Liang,

309
00:19:41,600 --> 00:19:43,000
even if you don’t kill him,

310
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:44,280
you should still banish him.

311
00:19:44,470 --> 00:19:46,070
Only in this way can we end the rumors

312
00:19:46,200 --> 00:19:48,820
and defend princess’s reputation.

313
00:19:51,020 --> 00:19:52,410
I agree.

314
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:54,070
I agree.

315
00:19:55,820 --> 00:19:58,040
I... I agree.

316
00:20:09,700 --> 00:20:10,460
No.

317
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:14,500
Yuanheng isn’t guilty.

318
00:20:17,020 --> 00:20:18,460
He made mistakes, but also contributions.

319
00:20:19,950 --> 00:20:21,340
It’s enough after he was banished for one year.

320
00:20:23,170 --> 00:20:24,860
I’m not going to banish him again.

321
00:20:48,620 --> 00:20:49,610
Liang Huaiji...

322
00:20:51,950 --> 00:20:52,610
Fine.

323
00:20:54,900 --> 00:20:56,900
You award him to use his original name.

324
00:20:58,970 --> 00:21:02,530
What contributions has he made?

325
00:21:12,570 --> 00:21:14,370
He saved my daughter’s life.

326
00:21:16,370 --> 00:21:17,890
Without his company,

327
00:21:18,750 --> 00:21:19,810
my daughter

328
00:21:20,520 --> 00:21:21,600
would have died

329
00:21:21,870 --> 00:21:24,420
in the marriage I picked for her.

330
00:21:27,820 --> 00:21:29,310
I’ll no longer banish him.

331
00:21:30,070 --> 00:21:31,100
I’ve decided

332
00:21:31,350 --> 00:21:32,760
where he would go.

333
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:35,390
You don’t need to worry.

334
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:44,910
You’re called Your Majesty,

335
00:21:47,470 --> 00:21:49,320
because you’re the Emperor of

336
00:21:49,570 --> 00:21:51,430
the whole nation.

337
00:21:53,470 --> 00:21:58,030
The whole nation is your home.

338
00:22:00,200 --> 00:22:02,830
All people are your children.

339
00:22:05,620 --> 00:22:07,560
How can you only love princess,

340
00:22:09,850 --> 00:22:12,710
and ignore all the other people?

341
00:22:14,670 --> 00:22:15,460
Your Majesty.

342
00:22:16,970 --> 00:22:18,470
Princess has a special identity

343
00:22:19,120 --> 00:22:20,710
and a eunuch bewitches her.

344
00:22:21,920 --> 00:22:23,720
Now, she can threaten you with her life

345
00:22:23,720 --> 00:22:24,740
to interfere with her family affair.

346
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:26,410
In the future, she can also threaten you

347
00:22:26,550 --> 00:22:28,260
so that she’ll interfere with politics.

348
00:22:30,170 --> 00:22:31,980
Being cautious against coups in the palace

349
00:22:33,370 --> 00:22:35,500
is always top priority of ancestral rules.

350
00:22:35,600 --> 00:22:36,650
What happened in Han and Tang dynasties,

351
00:22:37,070 --> 00:22:39,530
should be taken as a warning.

352
00:22:40,920 --> 00:22:45,610
Your Majesty, please banish Liang Yuanheng.

353
00:22:56,800 --> 00:23:00,410
Your Majesty, please banish Liang Yuanheng.

354
00:23:05,900 --> 00:23:07,610
So much for today’s discussion.

355
00:23:08,550 --> 00:23:09,340
You may leave.

356
00:23:11,670 --> 00:23:16,290
Your Majesty, I say it from the bottom of my heart.

357
00:23:18,520 --> 00:23:20,450
Please think it over carefully.

358
00:23:27,200 --> 00:23:31,130
Please think it over carefully.

359
00:24:09,750 --> 00:24:11,050
You want to resign?

360
00:24:12,870 --> 00:24:13,670
Your Majesty.

361
00:24:16,220 --> 00:24:18,210
I studied hard for a dozen years,

362
00:24:20,120 --> 00:24:21,800
not for a high position

363
00:24:22,850 --> 00:24:23,910
or a huge fame.

364
00:24:25,420 --> 00:24:26,955
I wanted to

365
00:24:28,870 --> 00:24:31,000
help a wise emperor,

366
00:24:33,670 --> 00:24:35,340
so that we could get united people,

367
00:24:36,250 --> 00:24:37,900
a peaceful nation

368
00:24:39,500 --> 00:24:41,040
and a prosperous life for people.

369
00:24:44,950 --> 00:24:46,130
Now, I’m too weak

370
00:24:47,785 --> 00:24:49,221
to persuade you

371
00:24:49,229 --> 00:24:50,564
to abandon your selfish love

372
00:24:50,572 --> 00:24:52,370
and be fair.

373
00:24:53,670 --> 00:24:55,180
In the future, I will

374
00:24:55,180 --> 00:24:56,270
make you be cursed

375
00:24:56,270 --> 00:24:57,810
for being unreasonable and unfair.

376
00:24:59,700 --> 00:25:01,130
When I can’t fulfill my duty,

377
00:25:03,250 --> 00:25:04,720
I’m too ashamed to live.

378
00:25:06,570 --> 00:25:14,000
I have to kill myself as an apology.

379
00:26:09,360 --> 00:26:10,640
Princess. Princess.

380
00:26:10,770 --> 00:26:11,860
You can’t get in, Princess.

381
00:26:14,620 --> 00:26:19,240
♪ You have made a simple bun ♪

382
00:26:19,970 --> 00:26:24,360
♪ You wear a light makeup ♪

383
00:26:25,070 --> 00:26:29,420
♪ You’re in a beautiful dress ♪

384
00:26:30,070 --> 00:26:30,760
Huirou.

385
00:26:30,760 --> 00:26:33,340
♪ You dance like the willow catkins ♪

386
00:26:33,340 --> 00:26:35,770
This is a poem

387
00:26:35,770 --> 00:26:37,120
Censor Sima wrote in early years.

388
00:26:37,120 --> 00:26:39,940
♪ I’d rather not see you ♪

389
00:26:40,500 --> 00:26:44,990
Princess. Princess.
♪ I’d rather to be merciless ♪

390
00:26:46,170 --> 00:26:47,380
Huirou, come back.

391
00:26:47,380 --> 00:26:49,240
♪ I sober up after the party ♪

392
00:26:50,850 --> 00:26:53,210
♪ It was quiet in the yard ♪

393
00:26:53,210 --> 00:26:55,060
Your Majesty, are you letting

394
00:26:55,750 --> 00:26:56,920
Princess come before so many officials,

395
00:26:56,920 --> 00:26:58,260
regardless of etiquettes?

396
00:26:59,620 --> 00:27:00,440
Princess.

397
00:27:02,420 --> 00:27:03,190
Princess.

398
00:27:05,620 --> 00:27:07,480
Come back right away!

399
00:27:11,670 --> 00:27:12,450
Huaiji.

400
00:27:16,470 --> 00:27:17,290
Princess.

401
00:27:22,450 --> 00:27:24,070
Who did you write this poem to?

402
00:27:25,170 --> 00:27:26,700
You loved someone?

403
00:27:29,600 --> 00:27:30,860
Where is the girl in your poem?

404
00:27:31,470 --> 00:27:32,330
Where is she?

405
00:27:32,690 --> 00:27:33,720
Did you abandon her?

406
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:36,470
Do you think

407
00:27:36,800 --> 00:27:39,090
all feelings are guilty?

408
00:27:39,920 --> 00:27:41,720
A man must live like a puppet?

409
00:27:42,870 --> 00:27:44,980
Father, Her Highness and I

410
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:45,940
must be

411
00:27:45,940 --> 00:27:47,320
the most beautiful puppets

412
00:27:47,620 --> 00:27:48,540
for people’s worship.

413
00:27:52,700 --> 00:27:53,720
You totally ignore it.

414
00:28:00,850 --> 00:28:01,850
You totally ignore it.

415
00:28:11,740 --> 00:28:12,570
Inside it,

416
00:28:14,170 --> 00:28:18,140
everything is broken.

417
00:28:21,500 --> 00:28:22,240
Princess.

418
00:29:03,270 --> 00:29:04,240
Do you think

419
00:29:07,350 --> 00:29:08,780
a princess like her

420
00:29:10,550 --> 00:29:11,340
is interested in or capable of

421
00:29:11,340 --> 00:29:13,580
interfering with politics?

422
00:29:15,250 --> 00:29:18,760
Can Yuanheng win her trust

423
00:29:19,320 --> 00:29:22,220
to get power or hurt our nation?

424
00:29:25,650 --> 00:29:26,850
Do you really think

425
00:29:27,750 --> 00:29:29,790
if my daughter wants to interfere,

426
00:29:30,150 --> 00:29:32,220
I will harm the nation for her?

427
00:29:36,070 --> 00:29:37,090
In fact,

428
00:29:38,270 --> 00:29:40,220
you all know I won’t.

429
00:29:41,950 --> 00:29:43,490
If I were so arbitrary,

430
00:29:43,550 --> 00:29:44,820
you wouldn’t have any chance

431
00:29:44,820 --> 00:29:45,840
to come here for remonstrance.

432
00:29:47,850 --> 00:29:49,740
If I didn’t care for my reputation,

433
00:29:50,850 --> 00:29:53,070
you wouldn’t have forced me by killing yourself.

434
00:29:54,320 --> 00:29:56,160
I’m loyal to Your Majesty.

435
00:29:57,720 --> 00:29:59,490
I know that.

436
00:30:00,900 --> 00:30:01,790
And I know

437
00:30:02,270 --> 00:30:04,030
you truly want to persuade me

438
00:30:04,120 --> 00:30:05,400
with your own life.

439
00:30:06,620 --> 00:30:07,770
In your hearts,

440
00:30:09,100 --> 00:30:11,220
it’s worthy

441
00:30:11,350 --> 00:30:12,820
when you can defend the authority of censors

442
00:30:12,970 --> 00:30:14,680
and make the Emperor accept advice

443
00:30:15,170 --> 00:30:16,980
with Yuanheng’s life,

444
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:19,160
your own lives

445
00:30:19,950 --> 00:30:21,140
or even my daughter’s life.

446
00:30:23,470 --> 00:30:24,210
At last,

447
00:30:25,770 --> 00:30:27,410
if the story of a modest emperor who takes advice

448
00:30:27,410 --> 00:30:28,787
can be written in history books,

449
00:30:29,700 --> 00:30:31,570
and become one of the ancestral rules

450
00:30:31,570 --> 00:30:32,920
to restrain later emperors,

451
00:30:33,750 --> 00:30:34,520
you will even

452
00:30:36,320 --> 00:30:37,330
sacrifice

453
00:30:38,620 --> 00:30:39,890
my life.

454
00:30:43,820 --> 00:30:44,540
Your Majesty.

455
00:30:45,320 --> 00:30:48,120
I don’t dare to hurt you even if I die.

456
00:30:59,370 --> 00:31:00,730
The censor system is set

457
00:31:01,900 --> 00:31:03,740
to supervise on the Emperor’s power

458
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:05,340
and restrain the superiors,

459
00:31:06,770 --> 00:31:08,990
so that they won’t hurt people

460
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,840
with decrepit, arbitrary, or corrupt policies.

461
00:31:11,500 --> 00:31:14,360
After all, we maintain this system

462
00:31:14,850 --> 00:31:16,410
for the people’s livelihood.

463
00:31:18,150 --> 00:31:21,210
Sima, don’t you think so?

464
00:31:21,970 --> 00:31:23,130
You’re right, Your Majesty.

465
00:31:27,170 --> 00:31:28,180
Since I was born,

466
00:31:28,950 --> 00:31:30,770
I’ve learnt to be an emperor

467
00:31:31,700 --> 00:31:33,770
and the father of everyone in our nation.

468
00:31:34,600 --> 00:31:37,040
I care for all people.

469
00:31:38,270 --> 00:31:39,960
But in my life,

470
00:31:40,800 --> 00:31:42,400
I seldom go out of this lonely castle

471
00:31:42,400 --> 00:31:43,300
for many times.

472
00:31:45,100 --> 00:31:46,830
I know about the territory,

473
00:31:46,830 --> 00:31:48,750
the nation and the people

474
00:31:49,550 --> 00:31:51,180
from the military reports,

475
00:31:51,420 --> 00:31:52,590
your proposals,

476
00:31:52,950 --> 00:31:56,050
tax revenues and disaster reports.

477
00:31:57,200 --> 00:32:00,080
From these proposals, I know

478
00:32:00,870 --> 00:32:01,870
whether my people are poor,

479
00:32:02,670 --> 00:32:03,660
whether they have hardship,

480
00:32:03,900 --> 00:32:05,070
whether they suffer from disasters

481
00:32:05,550 --> 00:32:06,740
and whether they live a happy life.

482
00:32:16,050 --> 00:32:16,940
And...

483
00:32:19,570 --> 00:32:21,830
Where are my people?

484
00:32:27,050 --> 00:32:27,990
My people

485
00:32:29,820 --> 00:32:31,430
are just around me.

486
00:32:33,350 --> 00:32:34,310
The eunuchs

487
00:32:35,120 --> 00:32:36,420
and the maids.

488
00:32:38,820 --> 00:32:41,330
Huaiji, who you think seduced his master,

489
00:32:44,100 --> 00:32:47,380
was born in a humble family in the Capital.

490
00:32:48,550 --> 00:32:50,510
He had his parents.

491
00:32:51,150 --> 00:32:53,840
His grandmother was kind
and his brother cared for him.

492
00:32:55,170 --> 00:32:56,210
But because...

493
00:33:05,950 --> 00:33:07,980
Because I wasn’t perfect enough,

494
00:33:10,170 --> 00:33:11,950
his father and grandmother died.

495
00:33:12,470 --> 00:33:15,080
He went to his uncle’s home with his mother

496
00:33:15,450 --> 00:33:16,750
away from his brother.

497
00:33:20,450 --> 00:33:24,130
Later, he lived there with his mother.

498
00:33:24,670 --> 00:33:25,800
He studied hard,

499
00:33:26,200 --> 00:33:28,420
expecting to pass the imperial exam,

500
00:33:28,420 --> 00:33:29,570
and be a useful man

501
00:33:30,770 --> 00:33:33,220
so that his mother could live a better life.

502
00:33:36,150 --> 00:33:37,440
But because of a plague,

503
00:33:38,770 --> 00:33:40,320
his mother died unexpectedly.

504
00:33:41,870 --> 00:33:43,650
A corrupt official colluded with his aunt

505
00:33:44,100 --> 00:33:45,570
and cheated him to be castrated

506
00:33:45,750 --> 00:33:46,780
when he was only ten years old

507
00:33:48,100 --> 00:33:49,860
just to get his mother’s legacy.

508
00:33:59,320 --> 00:34:00,600
This is the boy

509
00:34:01,270 --> 00:34:03,290
you want to sacrifice

510
00:34:03,290 --> 00:34:04,680
just to maintain the authority of censors

511
00:34:04,680 --> 00:34:06,410
and force the Emperor to accept advice.

512
00:34:08,470 --> 00:34:09,990
The eunuch who you think seduced his master

513
00:34:10,550 --> 00:34:11,460
is exactly a common person

514
00:34:12,470 --> 00:34:14,410
I can see with my own eyes.

515
00:34:14,970 --> 00:34:16,460
He was wronged and he suffered a lot.

516
00:34:17,050 --> 00:34:18,120
But he isn’t rancorous.

517
00:34:18,370 --> 00:34:20,360
He’s always nice to whoever around him.

518
00:34:21,370 --> 00:34:23,300
You think he instigated Huirou and Prince Consort

519
00:34:23,650 --> 00:34:26,120
and asked her to bully her mother-in-law.

520
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:28,940
Yet Prince Consort left a letter

521
00:34:29,020 --> 00:34:30,090
and worked as a witness,

522
00:34:30,090 --> 00:34:31,280
proving that Huaiji once helped him

523
00:34:31,280 --> 00:34:32,690
gain the affections from Princess.

524
00:34:33,370 --> 00:34:34,860
Huaiji even risked his own life

525
00:34:34,870 --> 00:34:36,010
to save Prince Consort’s mother in law

526
00:34:36,170 --> 00:34:37,680
from the fire.

527
00:34:42,250 --> 00:34:44,620
If I sacrifice

528
00:34:44,620 --> 00:34:46,370
such a kind boy,

529
00:34:47,100 --> 00:34:48,550
taking advice

530
00:34:48,920 --> 00:34:50,470
will be humiliating me.

531
00:34:54,570 --> 00:34:56,100
Maybe a real wise emperor

532
00:34:56,500 --> 00:34:57,890
must be decisive

533
00:34:57,890 --> 00:34:59,040
instead of hesitating.

534
00:35:00,250 --> 00:35:01,480
But I can’t do that.

535
00:35:02,970 --> 00:35:03,910
In my heart,

536
00:35:04,420 --> 00:35:05,760
I want fewer achievements,

537
00:35:06,350 --> 00:35:07,680
but more peace.

538
00:35:08,520 --> 00:35:09,860
I don’t want to see

539
00:35:09,950 --> 00:35:12,550
any innocent boy be sacrificed.

540
00:35:19,820 --> 00:35:22,430
I know what you mean, Your Majesty.

541
00:35:25,250 --> 00:35:26,520
In your heart,

542
00:35:28,270 --> 00:35:30,870
people matter the most.

543
00:35:33,300 --> 00:35:35,020
When Xixia disturbed the border,

544
00:35:36,100 --> 00:35:38,540
if you locked the border for one more year,

545
00:35:39,120 --> 00:35:42,060
a lot of Xixia people would have been dead.

546
00:35:43,150 --> 00:35:44,230
In the negotiation,

547
00:35:44,650 --> 00:35:46,220
we would have got better conditions.

548
00:35:48,620 --> 00:35:51,150
But you didn’t have the heart

549
00:35:51,200 --> 00:35:53,370
to see so many dead people

550
00:35:53,770 --> 00:35:55,630
even if they were from Xixia.

551
00:35:58,520 --> 00:35:59,610
During the reform,

552
00:36:00,620 --> 00:36:02,050
there were fewer redundant officials.

553
00:36:02,820 --> 00:36:04,090
Corruption was controlled.

554
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:06,270
When the reform went further,

555
00:36:06,920 --> 00:36:09,410
complains and political struggles occurred again.

556
00:36:09,570 --> 00:36:11,010
There were frequent disasters, too.

557
00:36:12,370 --> 00:36:15,550
You didn’t dare to continue the reform.

558
00:36:16,020 --> 00:36:17,210
Instead, you tried every means

559
00:36:17,210 --> 00:36:20,480
to protect executors including me.

560
00:36:22,620 --> 00:36:23,960
I think

561
00:36:28,800 --> 00:36:32,720
since the case is clear,

562
00:36:33,970 --> 00:36:36,110
and no one has done evil things deliberately,

563
00:36:37,270 --> 00:36:40,460
no one needs to be severely punished.

564
00:36:42,070 --> 00:36:44,810
Prince Consort asks to be transferred.

565
00:36:45,370 --> 00:36:46,860
Please approve of his application

566
00:36:47,770 --> 00:36:50,060
and give him properties

567
00:36:50,800 --> 00:36:54,220
to show your care for him.

568
00:36:56,570 --> 00:37:01,450
Princess fails to restrain her love

569
00:37:02,650 --> 00:37:03,950
and goes extreme.

570
00:37:04,750 --> 00:37:06,250
She should be the first to blame.

571
00:37:07,420 --> 00:37:11,120
But she has been sick.

572
00:37:12,020 --> 00:37:15,980
Let her stay in the palace for recuperation,

573
00:37:17,670 --> 00:37:19,760
but demote her and cut her salary.

574
00:37:21,900 --> 00:37:23,460
As for Huaiji...

575
00:37:24,700 --> 00:37:25,570
Yuanheng.

576
00:37:26,520 --> 00:37:28,200
I won’t banish him.

577
00:37:30,500 --> 00:37:31,520
I’ve decided

578
00:37:32,250 --> 00:37:33,510
how to deal with him.

579
00:37:34,900 --> 00:37:36,960
It’s not against any rules or ethics.

580
00:37:38,200 --> 00:37:39,780
You don’t need to worry.

581
00:37:49,250 --> 00:37:50,860
Demote Princess

582
00:37:51,050 --> 00:37:52,460
as Princess Yiguo.

583
00:37:54,120 --> 00:37:56,760
Prince Consort’s mother lives with Li Zhang.

584
00:37:57,800 --> 00:38:00,530
Li Zhang submitted Prince Consort’s letter,

585
00:38:01,000 --> 00:38:02,520
asking for divorce.

586
00:38:04,720 --> 00:38:07,750
Later when Huirou gets better,

587
00:38:08,250 --> 00:38:09,220
I’ll give an order,

588
00:38:10,870 --> 00:38:12,170
removing him from Prince Consort,

589
00:38:12,800 --> 00:38:15,050
give him two hundred gold as compensation

590
00:38:15,500 --> 00:38:16,650
and get him back to the Capital.

591
00:38:20,950 --> 00:38:23,060
All of you, get up.

592
00:38:30,700 --> 00:38:31,870
Thank you, Your Majesty.

593
00:38:39,250 --> 00:38:40,170
Sima.

594
00:38:42,020 --> 00:38:43,520
What else would you like to say?

595
00:38:46,300 --> 00:38:48,130
Your Majesty, I admire you most

596
00:38:49,320 --> 00:38:50,740
for your love to your people.

597
00:38:52,320 --> 00:38:53,360
In your life,

598
00:38:54,350 --> 00:38:55,670
you never want to kill any innocent people.

599
00:38:57,020 --> 00:38:59,440
You’re always generous and kind.

600
00:39:01,450 --> 00:39:02,770
Since Prince Consort proves that

601
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:05,390
Liang Yuanheng didn’t do evil things.

602
00:39:06,970 --> 00:39:08,630
You convinced me that

603
00:39:09,670 --> 00:39:11,000
I shouldn’t defend the authority of censors

604
00:39:11,320 --> 00:39:12,540
and the smooth channel of offering advice

605
00:39:12,900 --> 00:39:14,330
by sacrificing innocent people.

606
00:39:15,270 --> 00:39:18,360
You will certainly deal with Liang Yuanheng

607
00:39:18,950 --> 00:39:20,540
in a proper way.

608
00:39:21,900 --> 00:39:22,720
But...

609
00:39:25,320 --> 00:39:27,130
I don’t understand.

610
00:39:29,720 --> 00:39:31,290
Princess is poor.

611
00:39:32,550 --> 00:39:34,550
But it’s because she’s too stubborn.

612
00:39:35,402 --> 00:39:37,900
You marry her to your mother’s family

613
00:39:37,900 --> 00:39:38,600
to make it up for

614
00:39:38,600 --> 00:39:40,200
not taking care of your mother.

615
00:39:41,770 --> 00:39:45,000
Prince Consort is good at painting.

616
00:39:45,050 --> 00:39:46,060
He’s intelligent

617
00:39:46,060 --> 00:39:47,400
and honest.

618
00:39:49,150 --> 00:39:50,280
In such a marriage,

619
00:39:51,900 --> 00:39:53,610
what wrong have you done?

620
00:39:56,650 --> 00:39:58,900
Princess is wrong when she isn’t obedient.

621
00:40:00,370 --> 00:40:03,250
Why didn’t you teach her a lesson

622
00:40:03,470 --> 00:40:04,850
and send her back to her mansion?

623
00:40:05,420 --> 00:40:06,520
If you didn’t pamper her,

624
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:08,180
she would have defended her marriage

625
00:40:09,050 --> 00:40:10,360
as well as her title

626
00:40:10,950 --> 00:40:12,280
when she had no other choice.

627
00:40:13,500 --> 00:40:15,350
Isn’t that better?

628
00:40:58,170 --> 00:41:00,050
Because Huirou is a girl.

629
00:41:02,050 --> 00:41:03,670
She isn’t a puppet

630
00:41:04,920 --> 00:41:07,710
who looks perfect.

631
00:41:16,780 --> 00:41:19,860
= Sima Guang later becomes an important official of
Emperor Shenzong. =

632
00:41:19,860 --> 00:41:21,860
= He objected to the reform of Wang Anshi. =

633
00:41:21,860 --> 00:41:24,860
= And wrote History as a Mirror in later years.

634
00:41:32,475 --> 00:41:33,086
Your Highness.

635
00:41:39,670 --> 00:41:40,590
Danshu.

636
00:41:46,270 --> 00:41:47,130
Leave us.

637
00:41:47,290 --> 00:41:47,990
Aye.

638
00:42:17,050 --> 00:42:20,440
Zongshi is clever and cautious.

639
00:42:23,500 --> 00:42:25,440
He’s not bad at least.

640
00:42:26,800 --> 00:42:29,600
He won’t be a poor emperor.

641
00:42:31,900 --> 00:42:33,440
As for what a good emperor he can make,

642
00:42:34,550 --> 00:42:35,620
it also depends on his fate.

643
00:42:42,170 --> 00:42:44,010
After the problem is settled,

644
00:42:46,400 --> 00:42:47,660
I’ll be relieved.

645
00:42:56,050 --> 00:42:57,440
When you no longer worry,

646
00:42:59,200 --> 00:43:00,900
maybe you’ll get healthier.

647
00:43:34,490 --> 00:43:44,150
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

648
00:43:45,490 --> 00:43:53,830
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

649
00:43:56,670 --> 00:44:01,390
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

650
00:44:02,370 --> 00:44:06,530
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

651
00:44:07,970 --> 00:44:13,450
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

652
00:44:13,450 --> 00:44:18,240
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

653
00:44:21,900 --> 00:44:27,540
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

654
00:44:27,540 --> 00:44:32,450
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

655
00:44:32,950 --> 00:44:38,710
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

656
00:44:38,710 --> 00:44:43,800
♪ We only have each other in this cage ♪

657
00:44:44,230 --> 00:44:49,160
♪ Wish to fly freely in the next life ♪

658
00:44:49,780 --> 00:44:54,630
♪ Willows turn green flowers red ♪

659
00:44:55,320 --> 00:45:00,470
♪ Sing aloud with wine ♪

660
00:45:00,970 --> 00:45:06,010
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

661
00:45:06,550 --> 00:45:10,620
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

662
00:45:12,090 --> 00:45:16,730
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

663
00:45:17,750 --> 00:45:22,910
♪ The howling wind ♪

664
00:45:23,280 --> 00:45:27,350
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

665
00:45:28,830 --> 00:45:33,750
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

666
00:45:34,410 --> 00:45:39,630
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

667
00:45:40,050 --> 00:45:45,330
♪ The howling wind ♪

668
00:45:45,620 --> 00:45:50,520
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

669
00:45:51,110 --> 00:45:57,820
♪ Life is long yet joy is little ♪
